    "body": "@danra `using namespace ...` is not allowed (see `developer-notes.md`), and I'm afraid global prefixing would produce a gigantic diff. Just changing `{,u}int{8,16,32,64}_t` to `std::{,u}int{8,16,32,64}_t` would touch >2300 lines! :-)\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ git grep -E '[^a-z](u|)int(8|16|32|64)_t[^a-z]' -- \"*.cpp\" \"*.h\" | wc -l\r\n2363\r\n```",
